<p id="p0070">To measure the influence of the invasive shrub 
 <italic>N. glauca</italic> on the biodiversity of the invaded locations, the relative interaction index (RII) was calculated according to 
 <xref rid="b0055" ref-type="bibr">Armas et al. (2004)</xref>, using to the following formula:
 <disp-formula id="e0025">
  <math id="M5" altimg="si5.svg">
   <mrow>
    <mi mathvariant="italic">RII</mi>
    <mo>=</mo>
    <mfrac>
     <mrow>
      <mfenced close=")" open="(">
       <mrow>
        <msub>
         <mrow>
          <mi mathvariant="italic">Species</mi>
          <mspace width="5.0pt"/>
          <mi>d</mi>
          <mi>i</mi>
          <mi>v</mi>
          <mi>e</mi>
          <mi>r</mi>
          <mi>s</mi>
          <mi>i</mi>
          <mi>t</mi>
          <mi>y</mi>
         </mrow>
         <mrow>
          <mi mathvariant="italic">under</mi>
          <mspace width="5.0pt"/>
          <mi>c</mi>
          <mi>a</mi>
          <mi>n</mi>
          <mi>o</mi>
          <mi>p</mi>
          <mi>y</mi>
         </mrow>
        </msub>
        <mo>-</mo>
        <msub>
         <mrow>
          <mi mathvariant="italic">Species</mi>
          <mspace width="5.0pt"/>
          <mi>d</mi>
